I've raised this issue to continue our discussion on the previously closed PyIceberg PR on this parent repository. I've done some follow up research regarding the authorization flows since then, and I still believe that introducing an enhancement that allows our tools to fetch access tokens from a separate authorization server would encourage the adoption of the Rest Catalog even more.

